== Awards and nominations ==
{{main|List of awards and nominations received by Timothée Chalamet}}

Chalamet was nominated for the Academy Award for Best Actor for his performance in ''Call Me by Your Name''.<ref name="Oscars2017" /> He was also nominated for a BAFTA Award, a Golden Globe Award, a Screen Actors Guild Award, and a Critics' Choice Movie Award, all for Best Actor.<ref name="BAFTA2017" /><ref name="GG2017" /><ref name="SAG2017" /><ref name="CC2017" /> During the same awards season, Chalamet gained recognition for his supporting role in ''Lady Bird'', receiving nominations for the [[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Acting Ensemble]] and the Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture along with the rest of the cast.<ref name="CC2017">{{Cite web |last=Kilday |first=Gregg |date=December 6, 2017 |title=Critics' Choice Awards: 'The Shape of Water' Leads With 14 Nominations |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/2018-critics-choice-awards-nominations-list-full-1062824 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180220222516/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/2018-critics-choice-awards-nominations-list-full-1062824 |archive-date=February 20, 2018 |access-date=January 19, 2018 |website=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]}}</ref><ref name="SAG2017" /> For his work in ''Beautiful Boy'', he was nominated for a Golden Globe Award, a BAFTA Award, a Screen Actors Guild Award, and a [[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Supporting Actor|Critics' Choice Award]], all for Best Supporting Actor.<ref name="BB2019" /><ref>{{Cite news |date=December 6, 2018 |title=Golden Globe Nominations: Complete List |work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] |url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/golden-globe-nominations-2019-1203082075/ |url-status=live |access-date=December 6, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181206235056/https://variety.com/2018/film/news/golden-globe-nominations-2019-1203082075/ |archive-date=December 6, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=January 9, 2019 |title=EE British Academy Film Awards Nominees in 2019 |url=http://www.bafta.org/film/awards/ee-british-academy-film-awards-nominees-winners-2019 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190109113112/http://www.bafta.org/film/awards/ee-british-academy-film-awards-nominees-winners-2019 |archive-date=January 9, 2019 |access-date=January 9, 2019 |publisher=[[British Academy of Film and Television Arts]]}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=December 10, 2018 |title=Announcing the Nominees for the 24th Annual Critics' Choice Awards |url=http://www.criticschoice.com/2018/12/announcing-nominees-24th-annual-critics-choice-awards/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190802151427/http://www.criticschoice.com/2018/12/announcing-nominees-24th-annual-critics-choice-awards/ |archive-date=August 2, 2019 |access-date=January 9, 2019 |publisher=[[Broadcast Film Critics Association]]}}</ref>

